name: Gold & Silver Holiday Wine Gift Tag Printables
description:
Spread holiday cheer! These gold, silver, and black wine gift tags help add some festive fun to your hostess gifts this holiday season. 

NOTE: This order is for a downloadable PDF file. You will not receive any physical product, but rather a link to the PDF that you can download. 

All you need for this printable file is a computer, printer, Adobe Reader (which you can download for free at Adobe.com), thick white cardstock, paper cutter or scissors, and a large circle hole punch. If you don’t have a circle hole punch, you can always use scissors to cut out the hole for the wine bottle neck. Simply download the PDF file, print onto thick white cardstock, then cut along the inside of the edges of each design, punch a hole through the circle at the top for the wine/cider/beer bottle neck, fold slightly below the open circle, and gift. Gotta love easy holiday hostess gifts that are cute and fun to give and receive!

Cheers, friends! Let the holiday DIY fun begin!

* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * 
LEGAL: Urban Bliss printable designs are for personal use only. You may not use any part of these designs for commercial use. You may not share the downloaded files with others.

name: Honeycomb Wine Labels - Printable PDF
description: Send stylish good cheer, happy holidays or birthday wishes to friends, family and party hosts this season with Urban Bliss Printable Wine Labels! With this order, you will receive one (1) digital high resolution PDF file that contains two 4" x 5" images of the same exclusive Urban Bliss design. You can print as many as you like, cut, and adhere to your wine bottles! Note: Urban Bliss Media Printables are copyright protected and for personal use only. These files may not be altered, and they may not be shared or sold in any form. ORDER INFO 1. Place this item in your cart and place your order. 2. Then fill out this online custom order form with the exact text as you wish it to appear on the design AND your color choice for the center background color (see image sample to the left for color options). 3. Within 1-2 business days of completed payment, you will receive an email with a low resolution jpeg of your custom wine label design to review. After you give us FINAL APPROVAL, we will email you the high resolution 300 dpi PDF file. PRINTABLE TIPS 1. You must have Adobe Acrobat to download this file. You may download the software for free from Adobe.com. 2. Once you receive the file, you simply print onto adhesive labels (we recommend glossy or high quality matte full sheet 8.5 x 11" labels), cut, and adhere to your wine bottles. Print as many as you like! Please note: any additional design requests other than the custom text will require additional charges. COORDINATING ELEMENTS We can turn any of our original Urban Bliss designs into coordinating elements such as invitations, holiday cards, announcements, stickers, address labels, placecards, water bottle labels, and more! Just email us with what you need and the quantity. name: Madi Calling Card
description: Whether you're a busy mom on-the-go, a savvy professional in need of some starter business cards, or you're looking for a great gift for baby showers, birthdays, Mother's Day, and other fine holidays, our Signature Calling Cards are for you! The Original Mama Calling Cards (TM) designed first by Urban Bliss in 2005 and seen in hundreds of magazines and online publications since, have evolved into our Signature Calling Cards Collection. Modern, fresh & fun, our professional designs help any mom or savvy professional stand out from the crowd. One set includes 100 2" x 3.5" single-sided cards. Our cards are professionally printed onto luxurious, high quality, environmentally-friendly FSC certified Premium Cotton cardstock: 118# Cover/320 GSM. This beautiful thick cardstock is tree free, archival, acid free, recyclable, biodegradable and elemental chlorine free. ROUNDED CORNERS Bliss out your custom calling cards with modern rounded corners for just $5 more per set of 100 cards. ORDERING 1. Place the item in your cart and pay via PayPal (you can pay with a regular credit card; you do not need a PayPal account). Be sure to include a valid e-mail address with your order -- this is the e-mail address we will send the proof to. 2. Send an email to info (at) urbanblissmedia (dot) com and include all of the information you want included on the design written *exactly* as you wish it to appear (including punctuation, spaces, capitalization, etc). Please note space limitations based on the design you choose. 3. We will send you a digital proof via email to the email address you have used for your custom order form within 1-2 business days after receiving payment. 4. Your cards will go into print production within 1 business day of your email approval. Please note that no changes can be made after you submit your email with Final Approval. PRINTING & SHIPPING Our cards are professionally printed and will be shipped out to you via USPS within 3-5 business days from receipt of your final approval (arrival is usually between 5-8 days from design approval date). * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * Urban Bliss Life Blog | Twitter | Facebook

name: Premium Blog Header: Happy Dots
description: We find working with design clients absolute BLISS, but understand that you may not have the time, the budget, nor the need for a full design services. That's why Urban Bliss is now offering Limited Edition Web Graphics - graphics for your website or blog that you can purchase a la carte. Color options: Yellow/Grey, Pink/Grey, Aqua/Grey {click on the images at left to click through different color options. NOTE: the Urban Bliss watermark on the sample images will NOT appear on your finished custom header} Dimensions: 960 x 240 px Availability: 10 LIMITED EDITION URBAN BLISS WEB GRAPHICS Just because you're on a budget doesn't mean you need to sacrifice brand integrity. Your website/blog is a reflection of your brand, and we want to help you stand out with modern, fresh, fun graphics that will not be seen on dozens or even hundreds of other sites. By limiting the number of each design we make available, we help preserve your brand integrity while still making our modern web graphics accessible. HOW TO ORDER 1. Please be sure to choose a blog header that will accommodate the name of your website/blog. If you have any concerns, please send us an email with any questions before purchasing. 2. Place the item in your cart. 3. Payment is via PayPal. If you do not have a PayPal account, there is an option to pay with your regular credit card via PayPal. 4. In the Note to Seller in PayPal, please include your BLOG NAME/WEBSITE NAME and your TAGLINE (if you have one). 5. Please verify that the email address you have associated with your PayPal account is active; this is the email address we will send your JPG web graphic(s) to. 6. Within 1 business day, you will receive an email order confirmation from Urban Bliss, including any questions we may have regarding your blog/website name & graphic choice. 7. Within 3 business days, you will receive an email with JPG files of your custom web graphics. IMPORTANT INFO***PLEASE READ*** * These products are sold AS IS. There are no font options or color options other than the ones shown in the examples. This helps us keep the costs well below our standard custom design fees. * These products do not include installation; you are purchasing the graphics ONLY. * Due to the custom nature of these designs, Urban Bliss does not issue refunds for web graphics.

name: Chevron Valentine's Day Cards
description: To celebrate a day of love and friendship, send these sweet Valentine's Day Cards to loved ones. Or, if you have little ones, help them stand out from the sea of generic character cards with these unique, professional designs. Depending on how you cut the cards, each card measures approximately 3.5" x 4.5" and would fit into a 3.5" x 5" envelope nicely. * You will receive a PDF file in the email address linked to your PayPal account within 2 business days of your payment clearing. If you would like us to send your file to a different email address, please send us an email at info (at) urbanblissdesign (dot) com * Each PDF will contain four of the same design. * You will need Adobe Acrobat Reader in order to open the file * Print using your home color printer * Cut around the images Note: * The Urban Bliss watermark will not appear in the PDF file you receive. * A round corner punch may have been used for the cards pictured here. Usage: You may purchase, print, and distribute your prints for personal use only. No commercial use of any portion of the PDF file is allowed.
